'''Medfloss.org''' should provide a comprehensive and structured overview of Free/Libre and Open Source Software (FLOSS) projects for the [[:Category:health]] care domain. Moreover it should offer a platform to foster the exchange of ideas, knowledge and experiences about these projects.<ref>[http://www.medfloss.org/node/41 Mission Statement]</ref>

